<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> <unclear>maṟa</unclear>vaṉī<hi rend="grantha">śvaragṛha</hi> ttu <hi rend="grantha">mahāde</hi> varkkut tiruvamirtukku poḻutu <num value="10"><g type="numeral">10</g></num> A kkuttal Aññāḻi Āṉapaṭi muṉṟu poḻtaikku Arici pati<unclear>ṉai</unclear>ññāḻiyāl nel tūṇi Aññā ṭuriyāka vorāṭṭai nāḷaikku veṇṭu nellu nūṟṟu nāṟpatiṉ kalaṉe(k)y mu<unclear>k</unclear>kuṟuṇi nāṉāḻiyāl veṇṭu nilam Oṉṟe <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> māva<unclear>rai</unclear>k<unclear>ki</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>ḻākkiṉāl nel <unclear>mukku</unclear>ṟuṇiyāka <unclear>Ōrāṭṭ</unclear>ai nāḷai<unclear>kku ne</unclear>ṟ ṟoṇṇūṟṟuk kalattāl nila mukkāle muṉṟumā tiruvamirtu paruppukkup payaṟu nāḻiyā<unclear>l</unclear> nel munnāḻiyāka Ōrāṭṭai nāḷaikku <unclear>n</unclear>el patiṉoru kalaṉe mukkuṟuṇiyāl nila miraṇṭumāk kā<unclear>ṇi</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> nicati muppalamāka Orāṭṭai nāḷaikku <unclear>ti</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>yāl nila miraṇṭumāk kāṇi tiruvamir <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ku nicati nel Aṟunāḻi yuriyāka Oārāṭṭai nāḷaikku nel yirupattaiṅ kalattā ṉila<unclear>ṅ kā</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> nāḻiyāl nel loṉpati ṉāḻiyāka Orāṭṭai nā<unclear>ḷaikku</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> mukkalaṉe yirutūṇi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> n<unclear>ā</unclear>ṉāḻiyāka vorāṭṭai nāḷaikku <unclear>nel</unclear> patiṉaiṅ kalat <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ruvamirtu c<unclear>o</unclear>ḻikakkāy muppatun teriyilai muṉṟu paṟṟukku nel nicati Oṉpati <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ppattumuk kalaṉe yirutūṇik kuṟuṇiyāl nila <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> tirumeṉikkuc canta <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>muṉṟu poḻtaikku veṇṭuvatāl nel panniru kalaṉe tūṇi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Araikkāl tiruppaliccoṟṟuk kiraṇṭu poḻtaik karici yirunāḻiyā ṉi<unclear>ca</unclear>ti nelliṉā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kalaṉe yirutūṇik kuṟuṇiyā ṉila muṉṟu mā mukkāṇi nontāviḷakku paka leṭṭu Ira viraṇ ṭerivataṟku nicati <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>l munnūṟṟukkalattāl nila muveliti<hi rend="grantha">pa</hi> mālai <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <unclear>ti</unclear>ruppalikkuk kaiyviḷak kiraṇ ṭerivataṟku nicati ney muḻāk <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> nel <unclear>mu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> <unclear>ṟ</unclear>ṟoṇṇūṟṟuk kalattā ṉila mukkāle mu<unclear>ṉṟumā</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṟṟu<unclear>ṅ kāḷā</unclear><hi rend="grantha">ṣṭhami</hi> nāṉṟu naṟune <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> tiṅkaṭoṟuṅ kāḷā<hi rend="grantha">ṣṭhami</hi> k <unclear>kā</unclear>ṭiya <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> ḻiyāka Orāṭṭai nāḷaikku nel mukkalaṉe yirutūṇik kuṟuṇi <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṉṟu ciṟapputtiruvamirtu patteṭṭukkutta<unclear>l nā</unclear>ṉāḻiyāka <unclear>Orā</unclear>ṭṭai nāḷaikku nel kalane mukku<note n="331-1">The record is built in and incomplete.</note> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
